liver your valuable cargo to make a hefty profit... Just survive and reach for the warp gate! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 ships, 120 play cards, 34 equipment cards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore procedurally generated systems and fight your way to the warp gate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Encounter allies and foes, ancient civilization ruins, unlock powerful technologies and ships</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover and add new cards to your arsenal and increase your chances of surviving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pixelart by Kirokaze</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Synth-pop music made by Martyn Stonehouse</p></li></ul>",
